Class EarthServerGenericClient.Model_WCPSDemAlpha


Extends EarthServerGenericClient.AbstractSceneModel.
Scene Model: WCPS Image with DEM in Alpha Channel 1 URL for the service, 2 Coverage names for the image and dem.
Defined in: Module_WCPSDemAlpha.js.

setWCPSForChannelALPHA(querystring)
Sets a specific querystring for the ALPHA channel of the WCPS query. All red,blue,green and alpha has to be set, otherwise the standard query will be used.
Parameters:
querystring
- the querystring. Use $CI (coverageImage), $CD (coverageDEM), $MINX,$MINY,$MAXX,$MAXY(AoI) and $RESX,ResZ (Resolution) for automatic replacement. Examples: $CI.red , x($MINX:$MINY)
